<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真高兴看到你，火箭女孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们的原计划是要把你吸出学校。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个计划失败了。不过，幸好你还是来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们想要什么？”罗西问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪人博士咯咯的笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们想要除掉你，永远地！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他向罗西发射了一枚能量弹。嗖！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”罗西跳开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托挥着他的魔术棒。“变！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一面砖墙出现了。 砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”罗西跌倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！咚！机器人冲向罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只沉重的脚向罗西踩下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西抓住那只脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73788</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她用力把机器人往后一扔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哐当！大楼震动了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”怪人博士喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘校长看到墙在震动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89043</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有一个人看管他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89043</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所有人都回学校！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老师们和学生们赶紧出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100048</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托再一次挥动着魔术棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！罗西眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，普雷斯托在被激光击中之前就已经不见了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114295</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西觉得自己被甘草糖绳紧紧捆住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114295</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“抓住你了！”威格尔斯夫人大声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119064</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西挣扎着说道：“我讨厌甘草糖！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！一发能量弹把罗西打倒了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132412</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔在外面听到了里面的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132412</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西很危险！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从窗口爬了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托举起了魔术棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>呼！罗西用她的超级呼吸吹气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149926</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>魔术棒从普雷斯托的手里飞了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149926</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔抓住了它！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西笑了。“特勒尔！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别动！”特勒尔用魔术棒指着魔术师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162550</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>普雷斯托举起了双手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要对我念咒语！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170545</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>威格尔斯夫人丢下甘草糖绳，向门口跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170545</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你绝对抓不到我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快挣脱了绳子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她挥起甘草糖绳，抓住了威格尔斯夫人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不要！”坏人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190287</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听到了沉重的脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪人博士正向特勒尔跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200292</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿回我的魔术棒！”普雷斯托对着怪人博士大声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞！罗西的眼睛发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>机器人爆炸了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>怪人博士倒在地上，呻吟着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西赶紧把坏人们用甘草糖绳绑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她转向特勒尔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你帮我！你做好飞的准备了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔的脸亮起来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西一只手抓着特勒尔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一只手拎着被绑着的坏人们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”当罗西在美罗城上空飞的时候，特勒尔笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把犯人送进了监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，特勒尔和罗西回到了学校。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“罗西，特勒尔！”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们错过了所有的事情！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>坏人们绑架了学校所有的人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是火箭女孩儿救了我们！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269153</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”罗西做出吃惊的样子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269153</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不相信我们错过了那些！”特勒尔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>281917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两人咯咯笑起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>